		  (thanks Geoff Stewart)
	  - opus: refresh config template
	  - stream: add magic number for debugging (ref #514)
	  - ua: do ua_register explicitly (refs #508) (#509)
	  - ua: added ua param to message handler (#485) (thanks Juha Heinanen)
